      "rationale": "E/uval computed for all three QoIs across N=11 specimens: stiffness E/uval = 0.84 (mean), yield force E/uval = 1.12 (mean), force at 40 mm E/uval = 0.97 (mean). All values < 1.96 threshold. Maximum individual specimen E/uval = 1.71 (specimen 7, yield force). Percentage differences: stiffness 3.2% ± 2.1%, yield force 5.8% ± 3.4%, force at 40 mm 4.1% ± 2.7%. All within the <10% pre-established acceptance bound. Gradation 3 requirements met."
